[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0587","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0587.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0821","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9166,\"outputTokens\":16,\"totalTokens\":10846}}","description":"FreeBSD 系统下运行的 Seyon 2.1 rev. 4b（i586-Linux 版本）串口通信程序存在本地权限提升漏洞。该程序在处理 `-emulator` 命令行参数时未进行充分校验与边界检查，本地普通用户可通过在参数中指定恶意构造的程序路径来诱导 Seyon 以更高权限执行攻击者控制的代码。成功利用该漏洞后，本地用户能够获取特权账户权限，进而完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞仅影响安装了存在缺陷版本 Seyon 的本地主机，攻击前提条件是攻击者需拥有目标系统的本地登录权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0821"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.710","remediation":"升级到已修复该问题的 FreeBSD 系统补丁版本（1999 年 11 月后的 seyon 修正包），或执行 `chmod u-s $(which seyon)` 移除 seyon 的 setuid(root) 位以消除本地提权条件。若无法立即升级，应限制 seyon 仅由可信用户通过 sudo 运行，并移除不可信用户的执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/838","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/252","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe9e77bf3808998cc7ef33bc8a5ea311f35fadb0/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0821.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0821","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0821.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c8b0fec8b23470355b47059dbab5d2ebdfa2ac94/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0821.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-27fc-7vgc-cg5g/GHSA-27fc-7vgc-cg5g.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0821.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/838/info.html","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0587.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0587.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1178","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1178.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1550","title":"F5 BIG-IP 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"F5 BIG-IP 2.1.2 及早期版本的 bigconf.conf 文件处理存在任意文件读取漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 \"file\" 参数中指定目标文件路径，利用路径遍历漏洞读取服务器上的任意文件内容。该漏洞影响 F5 BIG-IP 2.1.2 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 5.0（中危），属于路径遍历类漏洞（CWE-22）。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，通过构造包含目录遍历序列（如 ../etc/passwd）的 file 参数值，即可读取服务器敏感文件，导致敏感信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1550"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-08","updated":"1999-11-08","remediation":"升级到 F5 BIG-IP 修复版本，并限制管理接口访问权限；临时缓解可在 Web 配置接口中禁用 file 参数功能，或通过访问控制列表限制对 bigconf.conf 相关接口的访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94217006208374&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94217879020184&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94225879703021&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7771.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/778"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1178.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1164","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1164.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1530","title":"Cobalt RaQ cgiwrap 虚拟站点权限隔离绕过漏洞","description":"Cobalt RaQ 2.0 与 RaQ 3i 设备上使用的 cgiwrap 程序未能正确识别运行特定 CGI 脚本所对应的用户身份，导致同一物理主机上不同虚拟站点之间的权限隔离失效。攻击者为具备某一虚拟站点管理权限的恶意站点管理员，可通过构造并访问特定的 CGI 请求，越权查看或修改其他虚拟站点上的数据。该漏洞利用无需普通用户身份，仅需站点管理员权限即可在本地多租户环境中实施跨站越权访问，影响在同一 Cobalt RaQ 系统上托管的所有虚拟站点的数据安全与隔离性。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1530"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-08","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"RaQ 2 用户使用 `rpm -U cgiwrap-raq2-3.6.4.C5.mips.rpm` 升级 cgiwrap 至 3.6.4.C5 版本，RaQ 3i 用户使用 `rpm -U cgiwrap-pacifica-3.6.4.C5.i386.rpm` 升级。升级后 cgiwrap 将正确识别用户身份并保持虚拟站点隔离。无法升级的用户应禁用 cgiwrap 服务或限制虚拟站点间 CGI 脚本目录的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94209954200450&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94225629200045&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7764.php","http://www.osvdb.org/35","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/777","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/9ce0ab809ed6d308ca08d3162931575004660698/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1530.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1530.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1164.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1164.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0663","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0663.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0863","title":"FreeBSD seyon 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统自带的 seyon 通信终端程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当程序处理 HOME 环境变量、-emulator 命令行参数或 -modems 命令行参数，或通过其图形用户界面（GUI）输入时，未对输入长度进行边界校验，导致特制超长输入可覆盖栈上返回地址。本地攻击者只需在启动 seyon 前设置恶意的 HOME 环境变量，或传入超长的 -emulator/-modems 参数，即可触发溢出并可能执行任意代码或造成程序崩溃。该漏洞影响存在 seyon 组件的 FreeBSD 系统版本，攻击需具备本地用户权限或能影响目标用户启动程序的环境，CVSS 基础评分 4.6，危害等级为中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0863"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-11-08","updated":"2026-07-17","remediation":"建议升级到包含修复的 FreeBSD 版本（FreeBSD 3.3-RELEASE 及之后已修复该 seyon 漏洞）。如无法立即升级，可移除或限制 seyon 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/X11R6/bin/seyon），避免以特权身份运行；同时限制普通用户对 HOME 环境变量及 -emulator/-modems 参数的可控输入，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0863","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5a67adc3536b9edff12a57c2de9cd5aa5d12653d/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0863.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fcr3-f7x4-9pjv/GHSA-fcr3-f7x4-9pjv.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0863.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0663.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1984","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1984.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1529","title":"趋势科技 InterScan VirusWall for NT SMTP网关缓冲区溢出","description":"趋势科技 InterScan VirusWall for NT 的 SMTP 网关在处理 HELO 命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送超长 HELO参数的 SMTP 请求，触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务崩溃或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Interscan VirusWall 3.23/3.3 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1529"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:38.173","remediation":"升级趋势科技 InterScan VirusWall for NT 到 4.x 或更高版本，并确保最新的安全补丁已安装。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94201512111092&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94204166130782&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94210427406568&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94199707625818&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94208143007829&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/55551","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/787","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3465","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/9ce0ab809ed6d308ca08d3162931575004660698/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1529.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1529","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1529.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f581b54f28a314b57ac171b83d3b2d21db7414a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1529.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/11845a9fe6e6b4d82150d9fd8a4257b88a244a45/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mmh6-2vw6-82r4/GHSA-mmh6-2vw6-82r4.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/interscan_dos.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1529.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/787/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--53e2c3f1-793e-42c4-ac61-c7fed198198f.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1984.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1166","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1166.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1533","title":"Eicon Diva LAN ISDN 调制解调器 HTTP 服务登录页面密码参数过长导致拒绝服务","description":"Eicon Technology Diva LAN ISDN 调制解调器的 HTTP 服务中，login.htm 文件存在输入验证缺陷。远程攻击者通过向 password 参数提交超长字符串，可导致设备 HTTP 服务崩溃或挂起，造成拒绝服务。攻击无需身份认证，利用难度低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1533"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-07","updated":"2024-11-20","remediation":"该设备已停止技术支持，建议升级到支持安全认证的现代设备；如无法更换，限制对调制解调器 HTTP 管理接口的网络访问，仅允许受信任 IP 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2024-11-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93846522511387&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/665","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3317"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1166.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1166.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1166.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1193","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1193.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1571","title":"用户要求为 CVE-1999-1571 生成 [title] 字段，需要中文漏洞标题，格式：「厂商 产品 漏洞类型」，20-100 字。 已知信息： - 漏洞编号: CVE-1999-1571 - 原标题: openserver 缓冲区溢出漏洞 - NVD描述: Buffer overflow in sar for SCO OpenServer 5.0.0 through 5.0.5 may allow local users to gain root privileges via a long -f parameter, a different vulnerability than CVE-1999-1570. - CVSS: 7.2 - CWE: NVD-CWE-Other - [avd] openserver 缓冲区溢出漏洞 分析： - 厂商：SCO（Santa Cruz Operation） - 产品：OpenServer - 漏洞类型：缓冲区溢出（Buffer overflow） - 影响：本地用户可通过长 -f 参数获得 root 权限 中文标题应该包含厂商、产品、漏洞类型。根据示例\"Microsoft Windows TCP/IP 远程代码执行漏洞\"，格式是「厂商 产品 漏洞类型」。 可能的标题： - SCO OpenServer 缓冲区溢出漏洞 - SCO OpenServer sar 缓冲区溢出漏洞 - SCO OpenServer 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞 根据示例，简短明了即可：\"SCO OpenServer 缓冲区溢出漏洞\" 或 \"SCO OpenServer sar 缓冲区溢出漏洞\" 由于描述中提到是 sar 命令的缓冲区溢出，可以更具体一些。但示例中也没有特别详细。让我保持简洁准确。 最终标题：SCO OpenServer 缓冲区溢出漏洞 等等，NVD 描述中提到 \"Buffer overflow in sar for SCO OpenServer\"，sar 是系统性能监控命令。所以更准确的标题可以是 \"SCO OpenServer sar 缓冲区溢出漏洞\" 或 \"SCO OpenServer 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞\"。 考虑到题目要求 20-100 字，\"SCO OpenServer 缓冲区溢出漏洞\" 是 12 字（含英文），可能有点短。但示例也是类似的长度。 让我再看要求：\"20-100 字\"。中文里一个字通常指一个汉字，英文单词可能按一个或多个字算。但示例 \"Microsoft Windows TCP/IP 远程代码执行漏洞\" 看起来也没有 20 个中文字符。 让我数一下示例： Microsoft (1) Windows (2) TCP/IP (3-4?) 远程代码执行漏洞 (7) = 大约 11-12 个单位 \"20-100 字\" 可能是指包括英文在内的总字符数，或者就是指中文字符数。不过示例显然没有 20 个中文字符。 重新看要求：\"中文漏洞标题，格式：「厂商 产品 漏洞类型」。示例：Microsoft Windows TCP/IP 远程代码执行漏洞。使用中文，20-100 字。\" 示例看起来不够 20 字，但也许他们不严格检查，或者英文算一个字？为了安全起见，我可以稍微扩展一下，包含一些关键影响信息。 比如：\"SCO OpenServer sar 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞\" 或 \"SCO OpenServer 系统监控工具缓冲区溢出漏洞\" 但我觉得保持简洁更符合示例风格。\"SCO OpenServer 缓冲区溢出漏洞\" 就够了。如果一定要更长：\"SCO OpenServer 本地缓冲区溢出提权漏洞\" — 这包含了影响（提权）。 让我检查一下：SCO OpenServer 本地缓冲区溢出提权漏洞 - SCO (1) OpenServer (2) 本地 (3) 缓冲区溢出 (4) 提权 (5) 漏洞 (6) = 6 个部分，但按中文字数算： S C O (3) O p e n S e r v e r (9) 本 地 (2) 缓 冲 区 溢 出 (5) 提 权 (2) 漏 洞 (2) = 23 个字符（含英文字母），如果按中文汉字算是 11 字。 我觉得这比较合理。但用户给的示例很简洁。让我再想想。 其实要求说\"20-100 字\"，示例 \"Microsoft Windows TCP/IP 远程代码执行漏洞\" 的中文字符是：远程代码执行漏洞 (7)，加上英文。总共长度也不到 20。 也许这里的\"字\"是指中文字符，示例只是示意格式，实际","description":"SCO OpenServer 5.0.0 至 5.0.5 版本中的系统活动报告工具 sar 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于该程序在处理命令行 `-f` 参数时未对输入长度进行边界校验，本地用户可通过构造超长 `-f` 参数触发栈缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址并控制程序执行流程，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞仅需本地低权限账户即可利用，危害限于受影响版本的本地提权场景，与 CVE-1999-1570 为不同漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1571"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:44.623","remediation":"安装 SCO 于 1999 年 11 月 5 日发布的安全公告 SB-99.17 中的 System Security Enhancement (SSE) 补丁包 SSE037，该补丁包含用于 SCO OpenServer 5.0.0 至 5.0.5 的替换 sar 二进制文件，可从 ftp://ftp.sco.COM/SSE/sse037.tar.Z 下载。如无法立即安装补丁，应临时删除或限制普通用户对 /usr/bin/sar（SetUID root 权限）的执行权限，以缓解本地用户通过 -f 参数缓冲区溢出获取 root 权限的风险。后续建议升级至 OpenServer 5.0.5a 或更高版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93762097815861&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94053017801639&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94183363719024&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=vuln-dev&m=102098949103708&w=2","http://online.securityfocus.com/advisories/1843","http://online.securityfocus.com/archive/1/27074","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/8989.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/643","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8cc4bd87e08227d0a597e9249036a66efd1a35dd/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1571.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1571","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1571.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3a7f9488e77673498ec37285be0a165ad71720f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1571.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-468j-4h4j-8vv2/GHSA-468j-4h4j-8vv2.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/643/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--96c29d61-6975-4ef5-bc9c-437c88134827.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000857.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-1571.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1193.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1056","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1056.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1340","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9162,\"outputTokens\":27,\"totalTokens\":10853}}","description":"Hylafax 是一款开源的传真服务器软件。该漏洞存在于 Hylafax 4.0.2 版本的 faxalter 命令中，由于程序在处理用户通过 -m 命令行参数传入的数据时未对输入长度进行充分边界检查，导致本地缓冲区溢出。攻击者若已拥有目标系统的本地用户权限，可通过构造并传入超长的 -m 命令行参数触发该溢出漏洞，进而提升自身权限至更高特权级别，可能获取系统管理员权限。该漏洞危害等级为高危，CVSS 评分 7.2，影响所有部署 Hylafax 4.0.2 版本的系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1340"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.947","remediation":"建议将 HylaFAX 从受影响的 4.0.2 版本升级到官方修复版本 4.1 及以上（通过源码重新编译安装或发行版更新包）。如无法立即升级，可临时移除 faxalter 程序的 setuid 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/faxalter），并通过 sudo 限制仅有 fax 组用户可执行该程序，以避免本地用户利用长 -m 参数提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94173799532589&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/765","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19590","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e244b55bdff85b2483c0e6a7cecd12f8bee0df6e/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1340.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1340","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1340.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/70f84d5684ed60f7a4d0750993d15c30e4fe3bbf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1340.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v39v-9hrp-c85p/GHSA-v39v-9hrp-c85p.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1340.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--21456e6e-7fb1-48a2-9fee-105cd610c68d.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1056.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0917","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0917.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1065","title":"Palm HotSync Manager 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Palm Pilot HotSync Manager 3.0.4 在 Windows 98 系统中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当 HotSync Manager 处于网络模式时，远程攻击者可通过向 14238/TCP 端口发送超长字符串，触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务拒绝响应，甚至可能执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Palm Pilot HotSync Manager 3.0.4 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。攻击无需任何身份认证，可在网络层直接发起。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1065"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:38.017","remediation":"将 HotSync Manager 升级至 3.0.4 之后的安全版本；如无法升级，将同步模式从 network 切换为 local（USB/串口），避免暴露 14238/TCP 端口；在防火墙层面阻止对 14238 端口的外部访问；或迁移至不受影响的 Windows 2000 平台运行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94175465525422&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1065.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1065","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1065.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1065.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j4fq-58mw-fvch/GHSA-j4fq-58mw-fvch.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1065.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88443/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a203bfc1-3574-4af9-ba7d-bcfe752d3798.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc"