，当恶意网站在 IMG_SRC 标签中嵌入超长字符串时会触发缓冲区溢出。攻击者只需在自身控制的网页中构造特制的 HTML 内容并诱导受害者（查看者）使用此软件浏览该页面，即可在受害者系统上执行任意代码。该漏洞影响安装并运行 IBM HomePagePrint 1.0.7 for Windows98J 的用户，攻击者无需身份认证，利用条件仅为诱使用户访问恶意网页，可实现远程代码执行，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1531"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-11-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:38.487","remediation":"建议立即卸载 IBM HomePagePrint 1.0.7 并升级至现代浏览器（如 Chrome/Edge/Firefox 最新版）及受支持的操作系统（Windows 10/11）。若必须保留该环境，请在防火墙层面禁止该程序访问互联网，并禁用浏览器中的 ActiveX/Active Scripting 功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94157187815629&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7767.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/763","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19588","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a3a08d51f200d453300fca8b852aada6b8c5985a/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1531.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1531","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1531.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/44e56ab96b4cc04024678e20a1f15145c3b3cc59/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1531.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gvcc-w8vm-24rf/GHSA-gvcc-w8vm-24rf.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1531.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e250aeb4-94ac-42ae-8a9c-bc2918488a72.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1985.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1985.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1985.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0742","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0742.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0948","title":"IRIX Solaris Turbolinux Canna输入系统 uum程序 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IRIX 6.5、Solaris 7.0 和 Turbolinux 4.2 系统中 Canna 输入系统的 uum 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞源于程序在处理输入数据时未对缓冲区边界进行有效检查，本地攻击者可通过传入超长字符串触发溢出，进而执行任意代码并获取 root 权限。受影响系统包括 IRIX 6.5、Sun Solaris 7.0 及 Turbolinux 4.2，攻击者需要具备本地访问权限才能利用此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0948"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-11-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:23.260","remediation":"升级到已修复的 Canna 输入系统版本（IRIX 安装厂商安全补丁、Solaris 应用 Sun 推荐补丁簇、Turbolinux 升级至 4.2 后续修正包）。在无法立即打补丁前，可用 chmod 0755 移除 uum 程序的 setuid root 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/uum），或限制仅授权用户访问以缓解本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/757","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19582","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0948.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0948","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0948.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/82035e540ee415f78310ba979a19dffd78d3cfa2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0948.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04